<text top="676" left="170" width="314" height="9" font="0">Ghana,  India,  Indonesia,  Kazakhstan,  Kenya,  Maldives,  Morocco,  Namibia, </text>
<text top="693" left="91" width="2" height="9" font="0"> </text>
